channel.title: Just Babbelen (Meh Site)
channel.description:
Well, thought I'd show off my website as Roger did, and yes, I got approval. If you don't believe me PM me and complain don't bring it on this thread, or you can just take it up with the mods. ;) Just Babbelen is a website focused toward chatting and communicating with other members of the site, however quite a bit of programming related things go down there :p. By registering you get access to our arcade with over 300 games, yes that's right 300 games. We are currently working on getting a private IRC server, and also a ventrilo server. This site has been around for about 4 months but was recently reset due to a forum software glitch. I encourage you all to at least visit the website. Also, if you have any suggestions to improve the site, please tell me here.
[b]Side note:[/b] Please do not go to Just Babbelen thinking it's a private server community, cause it's not.
You can view the site: [url=http://www.justbabbelen.com]here[/url] Or you can go straight to the forum: [url=http://forum.justbabbelen.com/index.php?referredby=1]here[/url]
Thanks, Anthony
